title: Can't Start Ranked 3v3
body: Every time I try to start a match, it won't let me invite people or start a match. What is wrong with it?

replies.body: Ranked Team matches are currently on a schedule, and doesn't appear to be up just yet.  Our schedule for each region can be found in our [Ranked Team Schedule](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/209964886-Ranked-Teams-Schedule) guide.  Hope that helps!
